#. type: Content of: <section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:6
msgid "Ticket States"
msgstr "Ticket Status"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:9
msgid "Predefined states"
msgstr "Vordefinierte Ticket-Status"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:12
msgid ""
"OTRS allows you to change predefined ticket states and their types, or even "
"add new ones. Two attributes are important for a state: the state name and "
"the state type."
msgstr ""
"OTRS erlaubt es Ihnen, die Ticket-Status zu verändern oder neue Status "
"hinzuzufügen. Hierbei gibt es zwei wichtige Optionen: den Namen des Status "
"und Typ des Status."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:16
msgid ""
"The default states of OTRS are: 'closed successful', 'closed unsuccessful', "
"'merged', 'new', 'open', 'pending auto close+', 'pending auto close-', "
"'pending reminder' and 'removed'."
msgstr ""
"Die standardmäßig voreingestellten Status lauten: 'neu', 'offen', "
"'erfolgreich geschlossen', 'erfolglos geschlossen', 'merged', 'entfernt', "
"'warten auf erfolgreich schließen', 'warten auf erfolglos schließen' und "
"'warten zur Erinnerung'. "

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:20
msgid "New"
msgstr "Neu"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:22
msgid "Tickets are usually in this state when created from incoming e-mails."
msgstr ""
"Tickets sind normalerweise nur in diesem Status, wenn sie von eingehenden E-"
"Mails neu erzeugt werden."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:27
msgid "Open"
msgstr "Öffnen"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:29
msgid "This is the default state for tickets assigned to queues and agents."
msgstr "Der Standardstatus für Tickets, die Queues und Agents zugeordnet sind."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:34
msgid "Pending reminder"
msgstr "Warten zur Erinnerung"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:36
msgid ""
"After the pending time has expired, the ticket owner will receive a reminder "
"email concerning the ticket. If the ticket is not locked, the reminder will "
"be sent to all agents in the queue. Reminder tickets will only be sent out "
"during business hours, and are repeatedly sent every 24 hours until the "
"ticket state is changed by the agent. Time spent by the ticket in this "
"status will still add towards the escalation time calculation."
msgstr ""
"Nachdem die Wartezeit abgelaufen ist, erhält der Ticketbesitzer eine E-Mail "
"zu dem Ticket. Wenn es nicht gesperrt ist, wird die Erinnerung an alle "
"Agenten der Queue verschickt. Erinnerungs-Benachrichtigungen werden nur "
"innerhalb der Arbeitszeiten versendet, und werden alle 24 Stunden "
"wiederholt, bis der Status des Tickets vom Agenten verändert wird. Die Zeit, "
"die dieses Ticket in diesem Status verbringt, wird dennoch bei der "
"Berechnung der Eskalationszeiten einbezogen."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:41
msgid "Pending auto close-"
msgstr "Warten auf erfolglos schließen"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:43
msgid ""
"Tickets in this status will be set to \"Closed Unsuccessful\" if the pending "
"time has expired. Time spent by the ticket in this status will still add "
"towards the escalation time calculation."
msgstr ""
"Wenn die Wartezeit abgelaufen ist, wird das Ticket auf \"erfolglos "
"geschlossen\" gesetzt. Die Zeit, die dieses Ticket in diesem Status "
"verbringt, wird dennoch bei der Berechnung der Eskalationszeiten einbezogen."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:48
msgid "Pending auto close+"
msgstr "Warten auf erfolgreich schließen"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:50
msgid ""
"Tickets in this status will be set to \"Closed Successful\" if the pending "
"time has expired. Time spent by the ticket in this status will still add "
"towards the escalation time calculation."
msgstr ""
"Wenn die Wartezeit abgelaufen ist, wird das Ticket auf \"erfolgreich "
"geschlossen\" gesetzt. Die Zeit, die dieses Ticket in diesem Status "
"verbringt, wird dennoch bei der Berechnung der Eskalationszeiten einbezogen."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:55
msgid "Merged"
msgstr "Zusammengefügt"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:57
msgid "This is the state for tickets that have been merged with other tickets."
msgstr "Status von Tickets, die mit anderen Tickets zusammengefügt wurden."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:62
msgid "Removed"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:64
msgid ""
"This is the state for tickets that have been removed by the customer. "
"Tickets will not really be deleted, they are just no longer shown as open. "
"In order to enable this state in the customer interface you need to add the "
"state type \"removed\" to the sysconfig setting \"Ticket::Frontend::"
"CustomerTicketZoom###StateType\"."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:69
msgid "Closed Successful"
msgstr "Erfolgreich geschlossen"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:71
msgid ""
"This is the end state for tickets that have been successfully resolved. "
"Depending on your configuration, you may or may not be able to reopen closed "
"tickets."
msgstr ""
"Endstatus für Tickets, die erfolgreich gelöst werden konnten. Je nach "
"Konfiguration kann es unmöglich sein, geschlossene Tickets wieder zu "
"eröffnen."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:76
msgid "Closed Unsuccessful"
msgstr "Erfolglos geschlossen"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:78
msgid ""
"This is the end state for tickets that have NOT been successfully resolved. "
"Depending on your configuration, you may or may not be able to reopen closed "
"tickets."
msgstr ""
"Endstatus für Tickets, die NICHT erfolgreich gelöst werden konnten. Je nach "
"Konfiguration kann es unmöglich sein, geschlossene Tickets wieder zu "
"eröffnen."

#. type: Content of: <section><section><title>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:85
msgid "Customizing states"
msgstr "Anpassen von Ticket-Status"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:87
msgid ""
"Every state has a name (state-name) and a type (state-type). Click on the "
"<link linkend=\"adminarea-states\">States</link> link on the Admin page and "
"press the button \"Add state\" to create a new state. You can freely choose "
"the name of a new state. The state types can not be changed via the web "
"interface. The database has to be directly modified if you want to add new "
"types or change existing names. The default state types should typically not "
"be modified as this can yield unpredictable results. For instance, "
"escalation calculations and the unlock feature are based on specific state "
"types."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:91
msgid ""
"The name of an already existing state can be changed, or new states added "
"through this screen. If the state \"new\" has been changed via the web "
"interface, this change also has to be configured via the config file "
"<filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename> or via the SysConfig interface. The "
"settings specified in the script below have to be modified to ensure that "
"OTRS works with the changed state for \"new\"."
msgstr ""
"Im Admin-Interface können Sie innerhalb der Einstellungen für \"Status\" "
"neue Status für die vorhandenen Statustypen hinzufügen oder ändern. Beachten "
"Sie, dass Sie bei Änderungen am Status \"neu - new\" auch die entsprechenden "
"Änderungen in der Konfigurationsdatei<filename>Kernel/Config.pm</filename> "
"bzw. mit Hilfe des grafischen Konfigurations-Front-End vornehmen müssen. "
"Folgende Änderungen müssen für einen geänderten \"neu\"-Status vorgenommen "
"werden:"

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><programlisting>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/states.xml:96
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [...]\n"
"    # PostmasterDefaultState\n"
"    # (The default state of new tickets.) [default: new]\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{PostmasterDefaultState} = 'new';\n"
"\n"
"    # CustomerDefaultState\n"
"    # (default state of new customer tickets)\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{CustomerDefaultState} = 'new';\n"
"    [...]\n"
msgstr ""
"    [...]\n"
"    # PostmasterDefaultState\n"
"    # (The default state of new tickets.) [default: new]\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{PostmasterDefaultState} = 'new';\n"
"\n"
"    # CustomerDefaultState\n"
"    # (default state of new customer tickets)\n"
"    $Self-&gt;{CustomerDefaultState} = 'new';\n"
"    [...]\n"

