msgstr "Z. B. 2010-11-20 00:00:00"

#. type: Content of: <section><table><tgroup><tbody><row><entry>
#: en/content/administration/adminarea/postmasterfilter.xml:82
msgid ""
"Sets the pending time of a ticket (you also should sent a pending state via "
"X-OTRS-State). You can specify absolute dates like \"2010-11-20 00:00:00\" "
"or relative dates, based on the arrival time of the email. Use the form \"+ "
