#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><note><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/email.xml:514
msgid ""
"Details about Postmaster filter processing are also present in communication "
"logs. Make sure to check <link linkend=\"adminarea-communication-log"
"\">Communication Log</link> in the Admin area."
