#. type: Content of: <section><section><para><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/email/smime.xml:256
msgid ""
"Configure a customer user backend to provide the attribute "
"<literal>UserSMIMECertificate</literal> with the customer user S/MIME "
"certificate (there is an example for LDAP customer user mapping in <filename>"
"$OTRS_HOME/Kernel/Config/Defaults.pm</filename>)."
